title: Édouard Manet Flowers in a Crystal Vase Eyeglass Case with Cloth
description:
Eyeglass Case developed from Édouard Manet’s Flowers in a Crystal Vase, 1882.

Eye spy artful inspiration. Protect your eye-wear in style and sophistication with our newest hard shell eyeglass case, featuring a detail of Flowers in a Crystal Vase, 1882. Matching microfiber lens cloth included.

  • Dimensions: Glass case- 6 x 2.5 x 1.5 in. Cloth- 6 x 6 in.
  • Material: Polyester.
